Revision history for App-Lilu

0.01    Date/time
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
        - EVE field extraction factored out of the run() POE closure into a
          testable parse_eve() method, with %App::Lilu::alert_columns as the
          shared source of truth for each table's column order.
        - Fixed the sagan_alerts INSERT listing "proto" twice, which
          PostgreSQL rejects with "column specified more than once".
        - Added tests for new(), read_config(), eve_instances(),
          get_short_class_snmp(), and EVE parsing (Suricata/Sagan/CAPE).

